articles.title: Sydney news: Former NSW deputy premier John Barilaro to face US trade role inquiry - ABC News
articles.description: MORNING BRIEFING: Former deputy premier John Barilaro will today appear before the inquiry created to investigate his appointment as NSW's trade commissioner to the Americas.
